A healthy diet is an essential part of everyday life. Do you want to join the ranks of healthy eating? This digital kitchen scale is the perfect companion. This professional scale designed for kitchen, mail room or even your workshop has a large round stainless steel washable tray for routine cleaning. It ensures accurate weighing even in high humidity areas. It has a splash-proof design making it is easy to use and perfect for all kitchens.

Features

-Made of high quality food grade ABS plastics, eco-friendly, durable and sturdy to use.

-Ideal for weighing ingredients, safe and non-toxic.

-Back hole enables scale to hang on the hook, saving space and keeping kitchen tidy.

-Anti-skid bottom design makes the scale stand stably in the kitchen.

-Digital display intuitively shows accurate readings.

-High-precision sensor provides accurate measurements and fast respond time.
